# Jiggon Custom Algorithm
# -----------------------
# You can write your own trading rules here in plain English.
# No coding required!
#
# Available Variables: RSI, MACD, ATR, EMA_TREND == BULLISH/BEARISH/MIXED
# Actions: BUY, SELL

IF RSI < 45 AND EMA_TREND == BULLISH THEN BUY
IF RSI > 55 AND EMA_TREND == BEARISH THEN SELL
